{"tid":974793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人喺德福m記撞過呢個癡線佬？","createTime":"2019-01-09T07:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T05:19:44.000Z","uid":222678,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"73b7b250fbc34b998e901bf93ab57ae8e0de81e2","tid":974793,"uid":222678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T07:04:18.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n琴日行九龍灣德福等人，見到有間m記就入去叫杯新地拎入去坐 坐咗喺個高枱喺度食<br />\n我好似平時咁，一路碌手機一路食，食到冇哂擺左個空杯喺隔離諗住坐多陣等frd<br />\n<br />\n我坐到咁上下，無啦啦有個廢中男人，瘦瘦地身高160左右黑黑地，攞住個餐盤企喺望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢微笑望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，乜野都冇講，同枱對面個個男人都望住佢，個眼神明顯示意：做乜撚？<br />\n<br />\n我冇理佢，其實我意識到佢係唔知杯雪糕係我食淨，示意緊點解你冇買野食就坐喺度，而且個個時間有好多空位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後佢死sip爛sip個餐盤係我同對面枱個男人中間啲位，撓住手繼續微笑望住我。<br />\n<br />\n過左幾分鐘，我忍唔住問佢 「請問發生咩事？」，佢繼續個個姿態微笑望住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我諗緊佢係咪聾啞人士，聽唔到我講乜又有啲咩需要。<br />\n<br />\n點知佢攞起電話唔知打畀邊個，對住電話講「以家啲年青人真係，冇買野食就大安旨意坐。」<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我即刻同佢講返，首先我有消費，我係咪要下下食完野坐多陣要大大聲同所有人講？ 二來間野咁多空位，你針住我做咩？第三請問有咩規定唔畀坐？先唔講由我食到件事結束都只係20分鐘<br />\n<br />\n無幾耐我朋友就打黎話行得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n想知家下係咪真係咁多廢中癡線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"665f6357fe20e8973f28e3cab40c391338192efd","tid":974793,"uid":7961,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T07:06:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好多傻人"},{"pid":"83c8560a98815ecfb53588fb4e3db53c4ea59127","tid":974793,"uid":107364,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T07:06:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19556771a03c60a83090303a5053bc51508d0dc7","tid":974793,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T07:06:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"060cb833804b729c42d3c3a157b377583fe3804e","tid":974793,"uid":45772,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T07:06:28.000Z","msg":"我嚟，宜家我就係擺到明要屌柒你呢啲九十後"},{"pid":"503cb2468ff5ca9a613c5d42ba63776cb163fcb2","tid":974793,"uid":222678,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83c8560a98815ecfb53588fb4e3db53c4ea59127","tid":974793,"uid":107364,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T07:06:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T07:07:37.000Z","msg":"我早半個鐘去到等朋友 10分鐘行商場 20分鐘成件事加order 有幾可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10500f4af44aac1b4f24ab0a095e8783a8c75484","tid":974793,"uid":222678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19556771a03c60a83090303a5053bc51508d0dc7","tid":974793,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T07:06:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T07:09:21.000Z","msg":"相信巴打夠後生既話 去幾轉個度打等 好快見到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"118d21f36ec68ccb0c8d4ed065b51f79437c9610","tid":974793,"uid":222678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"665f6357fe20e8973f28e3cab40c391338192efd","tid":974793,"uid":7961,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T07:06:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好多傻人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T07:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌"},{"pid":"a1ad3f63011386724cfaa50f8c62febeaeb45746","tid":974793,"uid":222678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T17:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b23b6475832b67bd2f49291da8921835e95ce9cc","tid":974793,"uid":1506